dialogues:
We were just floatin by,
gathering some
Eucalyptus cloves...

when we heard that
glourious SOUND, man.

We are the
Voice of the Australiabear.

We watch over this train
in search of the worthy
and the RIGHTEOUS Ones
on their way to
Lyublianahh.

We seek to aid you by
sharing in these magical
cloves that we gather...

But before the
herb is granted,
we must inquire...

How doth one sculpt
such RADICAL TONES,
my guy?

See those boxes
on the floor?
